description: President Andrzej Duda comes top but fails to take enough votes to win the election outright.
title: Poland presidential election heads for second round
title_page: Poland presidential election heads for second round - BBC News
maintext: Polityka weekly says Andrzej Duda's performance augurs well for the incumbent president: "There has never been a time when a candidate with such an advantage in the first round went on to lose in the second."
